**To import a client certificate revocation list**

The following ``import-client-vpn-client-certificate-revocation-list`` example imports a CRL to the specified Client VPN endpoint. ::

    aws ec2 import-client-vpn-client-certificate-revocation-list \
        --client-vpn-endpoint-id cvpn-endpoint-123456789123abcde \
        --certificate-revocation-list dummyCRLdata

Output::

    {
        "Return": true
    }
